name: Spy No More
description:
The Spy No More Camera Cling is a removable, reusable, nontransparent static cling webcam cover that can protect you from cyber spying and stalking. 

In other words, it forces online peeping toms to peep somewhere else.

Every $5.00 order includes 3 Camera Clings, which are perfect for most laptops, tablets, smart TVs and smartphones.
